Sudo yum update --to update current machine 
Navigate to Opt directory and paste download link from Splunk Website (Wget -O ..........)
Do an Ls to see dowloaded package
Do a sudo yum install followed by package name to install
Start  package by : sudo /opt/splunk/bin/splunk start
Incase you downloaded a UF do : sudo /opt/splunkforwarder/bin/splunk start
